    { type: 'strategy', text: '已发过轻量跟进，下次给价值信息而非催单：材质差异化（100% cotton knitted预洗不缩水）、DDP到门便利性（无隐藏关税）、工厂背书（Disney/帮宝适）。如果客户觉得贵，给一个12pcs试单降门槛方案。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: 'Hi Mohammed! Just wanted to share — our 100% cotton knitted romper uses pre-washed fabric that won\'t shrink, unlike many market alternatives. Plus $70 DDP means no surprise customs fees — everything delivered to your door. We\'re the factory behind Pampers Olympic Edition and Disney baby lines. If 24pcs is tight on budget, I can suggest a 12pcs trial: $8.20×12+$45 DDP=$143.40. What do you think?' },
    { type: 'trigger', text: '5天仍不回复→确认价格敏感，提供混纺降级方案($5.50-6.50/pc)；10天不回复→归档待激活' },
  ], { color: C.orange, bgColor: C.orangeBg, icon: '🟠' }));

  children.push(...Card('8. Aula Alsaad  |  阿拉伯国家  |  B级  |  产品切换中·需重新引导', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: '两段对话：①Apr 1问春夏秋冬款+各种颜色尺码，我方说"500件起订"+"不能直接给价"→客户说"منتجات عادية"(普通产品)→对话卡住；②Apr 26客户重新发了3个新产品卡片（Thermal Pajama Set, Custom Kids Set, Baby Floral Pajamas），我方简单反问"كم الكمية؟"。客户可能在比多个产品，没决定选哪个。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '针对3个新产品逐一简要回应：有现货/价格范围/MOQ。推荐一个最畅销的作为切入点（Custom Kids Set），降低决策负担。不要一次问太多问题。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: 'مرحباً! بالنسبة للمنتجات الثلاثة: 1. طقم البيجاما الحراري: متوفر، $3.0-3.5/قطعة 2. طقم الأطفال القطني: متوفر، $2.8-3.2/قطعة — الأكثر مبيعاً هذا الموسم 3. بيجاما الأزهار للبنات: متوفر، $2.5-3.0/قطعة. جميعها بمقاسات 80-120 سم. سأرسل لك صور الطقم القطني (الأكثر مبيعاً) أولاً. أي منها تفضل أن أرسل لك عرض سعر مفصل له؟' },
    { type: 'trigger', text: '客户选产品→发详细报价+运费；3天不回复→发最畅销款产品图激活' },
  ], { color: C.orange, bgColor: C.orangeBg, icon: '🟠' }));

  children.push(...Card('9. Susuanna ParkerAdentwi  |  加纳(广州收货仓)  |  B级  |  已报价·待付款', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: '客户给了广州白云区详细地址(POG-ARABA PARKER)，典型的非洲贸易公司中国集货仓。已报价$4.39×10=$46.90+$3运费，Apr 27我方说"After confirmation, I will create an order"。UNREAD状态。10件量极小→试单，$3是广州本地运费。已经到了付款环节，不要多问。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '直接推进成交：发PI，确认尺寸颜色，问付款方式。已经到最后一公里了，多问问题只会增加流失风险。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: 'Hi! Your order is ready: • Thermal Pajama Set × 10pcs • $4.39/pc + $3 shipping = $46.90 total • Shipping to: 广州白云区大朗北路68号. PI is prepared. Just confirm: 1) Payment: TT or Trade Assurance? 2) Sizes/colors as discussed? Once confirmed, I\'ll ship within 1-3 days. 😊' },
    { type: 'trigger', text: '确认付款→1-3天发货；3天不回复→发PI截图再次提醒' },
  ], { color: C.orange, bgColor: C.orangeBg, icon: '🟠' }));

  children.push(...Card('10. rehema kiseyu  |  坦桑尼亚  |  A级  |  样品方案已发·等客户确认', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: '16色×4码各1件=测试样品单。我方Apr 28发了非常详细的样品方案（16色样品生产5-7天、样品费可退、需要确认地址/包装/印花）。刚发完方案，现在催会显得pushy。分类器因"quality"关键词误判为售后——实际是正常样品询盘。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '等3天后发轻量价值跟进：新到面料/新图案选项/类似客户案例。不要问"决定了吗"，给新的有价值信息让客户自然地回来。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: '（3天后发送）Hi Rehema! Quick update — we just received new fabric prints for the kids sport set collection. If you\'d like, I can add these new patterns to your sample set at no extra charge — more options for your market. No rush on your decision — samples are ready whenever you are. 😊' },
    { type: 'trigger', text: '3天后发上述跟进；7天不回复→问是否需要调整方案（减少颜色/先打一半）；14天不回复→归档待激活' },
  ], { color: C.orange, bgColor: C.orangeBg, icon: '🟠' }));

  // ==================== 四、P2 本周内处理 ====================
  children.push(Divider());
  children.push(Section('四、P2 本周内处理', C.yellow));

  children.push(...Card('11. Cindy Nadal  |  法语区  |  B级  |  报价$68 DDP·6件量太小', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: '客户要6件，我方报价$68 DDP空运15天。6件×$3=$18商品+$68运费=$86，运费是货值的近4倍，客户可能被运费吓到了。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '推荐增加到20件摊薄运费，同时给海运选项（便宜但慢）。让客户感觉有选择权而不是被动接受高价运费。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: 'Bonjour! Une suggestion — pour 6 pièces, le fret DDP ($68) pèse lourd. Si vous passez à 20 pièces: • Prix unitaire: $2.80/pc • Fret DDP: $75 (presque le même prix) • Total: $131 (environ $6.55/pc tout compris). Ou pour 6 pièces, le fret maritime est disponible (~$30, 25-30 jours). Qu\'en pensez-vous?' },
  ], { color: C.yellow, bgColor: C.yellowBg, icon: '🟡' }));

  children.push(...Card('12. Sifa Vano  |  国家未知  |  C级  |  个人买家·需确认身份', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: '发了4个产品卡片，回复简短（"personal", "I am own"）。大概率是个人买家给孩子买，不是B2B批发。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '直接确认身份。如果是店主→小B方案（5pcs起订）；如果个人→礼貌说明MOQ限制但可以推荐零售渠道。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: 'Hi! Just to clarify — are you buying for your own child, or are you a small shop owner looking to resell? If you\'re a shop owner, our MOQ starts from 5pcs per design with starter packs. If it\'s personal use, I can recommend some retail channels. Let me know!' },
  ], { color: C.yellow, bgColor: C.yellowBg, icon: '🟡' }));

  children.push(...Card('13. Regina Kabanda  |  国家未知  |  C级  |  基础询盘·2岁婴儿连体衣', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: '客户问珊瑚绒连体衣有没有2岁宝宝的。我方确认有90cm并问了数量。客户未回。需求简单明确。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '轻量跟进，给产品详情（材质/尺码/价格/现货），直接推动下单。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: 'Hi! The coral fleece onesie for 2-year-old (size 90cm) is in stock: • Material: Coral fleece, soft & warm • Size: 90cm (fits 18-24 months) • Price: $4.00/pc • MOQ: 5pcs • Ready to ship in 1-3 days. How many would you like? I can calculate shipping for you.' },
  ], { color: C.yellow, bgColor: C.yellowBg, icon: '🟡' }));

  children.push(...Card('14. Adm Reda  |  阿拉伯国家  |  C级  |  要8岁尺码·2套', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: '客户要8岁(150cm)睡衣套装，2套。我方解释了按身高比年龄准，说"问经理确认"。后无回复。量极小可能是个人买家。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '直接报价+确认。不要多问，给价格和现货状态。2套低于MOQ可灵活处理。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: 'مرحباً! بالنسبة لطقم البيجاما مقاس 150 سم (8 سنوات): • السعر: $4.35/طقم • متوفر في المخزون • يمكن شحن طقمين. هل تريد المتابعة؟ أحتاج فقط تأكيد عنوان الشحن.' },
  ], { color: C.yellow, bgColor: C.yellowBg, icon: '🟡' }));

  children.push(...Card('15. Sayfullaeva Shahnoza  |  国家未知  |  C级  |  ⚠️Scraper名错·已发详细回复', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: 'Scraper名为"AnneMarie Nsomp"，实际发送者"Sayfullaeva Shahnoza"。客户发了1件90cm女孩家居服，我方Apr 24发了完整工厂介绍（Disney/强生/帮宝适）。回复质量好，等客户反应即可。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '已发了高质量回复，不需要立即跟进。本周内发一条轻量新品推荐，不催。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: '（本周内发送）Hi Shahnoza! Hope you\'re well. We\'ve just added new summer prints for our girls homewear collection. Happy to share the latest designs if you\'re still looking. No pressure at all!' },
  ], { color: C.yellow, bgColor: C.yellowBg, icon: '🟡' }));

  children.push(...Card('16. maimouna cisse  |  法语区  |  C级  |  ⚠️Scraper名错·围兜询盘', [
    { type: 'diagnosis', text: 'Scraper名为"Conteza Elias"，实际发送者"maimouna cisse"。客户发了婴儿围兜产品卡($0.45-0.50, MOQ 10pcs)。我方Apr 23发了法语跟进。围兜试单成本极低。' },
    { type: 'strategy', text: '轻量法语跟进。围兜试单几乎零风险（10件仅$5），给一个打包试单+西非运费估算。' },
    { type: 'reply', text: 'Bonjour Maimouna! Pour tester nos bavoirs, c\'est vraiment sans risque: 10 pièces à $0.50 = $5.00 seulement! Je peux vous envoyer les 3 motifs les plus vendus. Fret vers l\'Afrique de l\'Ouest: ~$25-30. Total: ~$35 pour 10 bavoirs livrés. Voulez-vous essayer?' },
  ], { color: C.yellow, bgColor: C.yellowBg, icon: '🟡' }));

  // ==================== 五、P3 低活跃 ====================
  children.push(Divider());
  children.push(Section('五、P3 低活跃客户（本周统一处理）', C.light));

  const lowActive = [
    { name: 'TheodoraAdelaide Mahe', note: '1个产品卡+法语自动模板，无互动', action: '本周发法语畅销款推荐激活' },
    { name: 'Fathima (User name)', note: '印度。价格严重不匹配($5.60 vs <$2.13)，客户说"Ok thankyou"后离开', action: '推荐$2以内替代品，最后一次尝试；不复则归档' },
    { name: 'Jemima Piema', note: '仅2条消息（产品卡+法语模板）', action: '发法语工厂优势简介+畅销目录' },
    { name: 'Assiatou Barry', note: '4条消息，法语模板已发，无互动', action: '标准激活流程' },
    { name: 'Lohgah Sharon', note: '仅2条消息，无实质互动', action: '暂不处理，观察1个月' },
    { name: '同行推销(User name)', note: '中国工厂来推销，不是我方客户', action: '礼貌回复+不深入沟通' },
  ];

  for (const c of lowActive) {
    children.push(
      new Paragraph({
        children: [
          T(c.name, { size: 20, bold: true, color: C.ink }),
          T('  —  ' + c.note, { size: 18, color: C.soft }),
          T('  → ' + c.action, { size: 17, color: C.accent }),
        ],
        spacing: { before: 40, after: 20 },
        indent: { left: 200 },
      }),
    );
  }

  // ==================== 六、执行检查清单 ====================
  children.push(Divider());
  children.push(Section('六、今日执行检查清单', C.green));

  const checklist = [
    { done: false, text: 'amer ly — 发阿拉伯语消息推进付款（确认现货+付款方式选择）', pri: 'P0' },
    { done: false, text: 'azaan ss — 重新开启对话，200pcs $3.80报价+面料价值信息', pri: 'P0' },
    { done: false, text: 'zainab Babesets — 帮客户简化选择，确认最感兴趣的产品后深入报价', pri: 'P0' },
    { done: false, text: 'Amal Alamhrooqi (arshavin amoah) — 消除清关恐惧，推动确认DAP成交', pri: 'P0 紧急' },
    { done: false, text: 'Ahmed Darrat — 承认混乱，确认产品，直接回答RMB价格问题', pri: 'P0' },
    { done: false, text: 'Krisgel Igros — 补全运费信息，发30pcs打包estimate', pri: 'P1' },
    { done: false, text: 'fernande Pochette (Mohammed) — 发产品价值信息+12件试单方案', pri: 'P1' },
    { done: false, text: 'Aula Alsaad — 回应3个新产品卡片，推荐最畅销款', pri: 'P1' },
    { done: false, text: 'Susuanna ParkerAdentwi — 发PI+确认付款方式', pri: 'P1' },
    { done: false, text: 'rehema kiseyu — 等3天后发新面料轻量跟进', pri: 'P1' },
    { done: false, text: 'Cindy Nadal — 推荐20件方案摊薄运费', pri: 'P2' },
    { done: false, text: 'Sifa Vano — 确认身份（个人还是店主）', pri: 'P2' },
    { done: false, text: 'Regina Kabanda + Adm Reda — 直接报价+现货确认', pri: 'P2' },
    { done: false, text: 'Sayfullaeva Shahnoza + maimouna cisse — 法语轻量跟进', pri: 'P2' },
    { done: false, text: '6个低活跃客户 — 统一发标准激活消息', pri: 'P3' },
  ];

  for (const item of checklist) {
    const priColor = item.pri.startsWith('P0') ? C.red : item.pri.startsWith('P1') ? C.orange : C.yellow;
    children.push(
      new Paragraph({
        children: [
          T('☐ ', { size: 22, color: C.light }),
          T(item.text, { size: 19, color: C.ink }),
          T('  [' + item.pri + ']', { size: 16, bold: true, color: priColor }),
        ],
        spacing: { before: 20, after: 30 },
        indent: { left: 200 },
      }),
    );
  }

  // ==================== 七、系统问题 & 改进建议 ====================
  children.push(Divider());
  children.push(Section('七、系统问题 & 改进建议', C.purple));

  const reminders = [
    'Scraper名字提取Bug（严重）：3个客户名字错误 — arshavin amoah→Amal Alamhrooqi, Conteza Elias→maimouna cisse, AnneMarie Nsomp→Sayfullaeva Shahnoza。需修复scraper.mjs中名字提取逻辑',
    '分类器误判：rehema kiseyu和azaan ss因含"quality"关键词被分到after_sales，实际是样品询盘和询价。关键词"quality"不应单独触发after_sales',
    '回复流程问题：多次出现"I\'ll check with manager"然后客户等太久。建议为常见产品制定标准报价区间，减少等待时间',
    '模板使用时机：3-question模板对已发具体产品卡片的客户不适用——客户已告诉你要什么，先报价再问补充信息',
    'Amal Alamhrooqi（arshavin amoah）上一轮完全遗漏：UNREAD状态+20条消息却被跳过，需要确保后续所有客户都被覆盖',
    '现货vs定制判定：多个客户问了现货问题，产品卡写"In Stock"但我方是否真有库存需要确认。这是客户决策的关键信息',
  ];

  for (const r of reminders) {
    children.push(
      new Paragraph({
        children: [T('• ' + r, { size: 18, color: C.soft })],
        spacing: { before: 20, after: 30 },
        indent: { left: 200 },
      }),
    );
  }

  // ==================== 附录 ====================
  children.push(Divider());
  children.push(Section('附录：跟进优先级排序逻辑', C.light));

  children.push(
    new Paragraph({
      children: [T('排序维度：客户明确度 > 时效性 > 订单规模 > 市场价值', { size: 18, color: C.soft })],
      spacing: { after: 60 },
    }),
    new Paragraph({
      children: [T('• S级（今日必回）：客户已明确需求且在等回复，不回复即丢失。典型：已报价待确认、多次追问、已进入付款/物流讨论', { size: 18, color: C.ink })],
      spacing: { after: 30 }, indent: { left: 200 },
    }),
    new Paragraph({
      children: [T('• A级（今日回）：客户有明确互动但进展早期，需要报价或补充信息来推进', { size: 18, color: C.ink })],
      spacing: { after: 30 }, indent: { left: 200 },
    }),
    new Paragraph({
      children: [T('• B级（48h内回）：有互动但客户不急于回复，或我方已发完整信息只需等待', { size: 18, color: C.ink })],
      spacing: { after: 30 }, indent: { left: 200 },
    }),
    new Paragraph({
      children: [T('• C级（本周内回）：低活跃/试探性客户，统一批量激活', { size: 18, color: C.ink })],
      spacing: { after: 60 }, indent: { left: 200 },
    }),
    new Paragraph({
      children: [T('定价公式：成本(RMB) ÷ 0.6 ÷ 6.8 = USD报价（覆盖国际站运营成本），向上取整。例：15.2÷0.6÷6.8 = $3.72 → 报价$3.80', { size: 18, color: C.orange, italics: true })],
      spacing: { after: 60 }, indent: { left: 200 },
    }),
  );

  // ==================== 页脚 ====================
  children.push(Divider());
  children.push(
    new Paragraph({
      children: [T('小星星服饰 · 小满CRM客户跟进方案 · ' + `${now.getFullYear()}/${now.getMonth() + 1}/${now.getDate()}`, { size: 16, color: C.light })],
      alignment: AlignmentType.CENTER,
      spacing: { before: 200 },
    }),
    new Paragraph({
      children: [T('所有回复话术为中文参考版本，实际发送请根据对应客户语言翻译后使用', { size: 15, color: C.light })],
      alignment: AlignmentType.CENTER,
      spacing: { after: 200 },
    }),
  );

  // ==================== 构建文档 ====================
  const doc = new Document({
    creator: '小满CRM助手',
    title: '小满CRM客户执行方案',
    description: '专业客户跟进策略分析与回复话术',
    styles: {
      default: {
        document: {
          run: { size: 21, font: 'Microsoft YaHei' },
        },
      },
    },
    sections: [{
      properties: {
        page: {
          margin: { top: 1200, bottom: 1200, left: 1400, right: 1400 },
        },
      },
      children,
    }],
  });

  const ts = `${now.getFullYear()}${String(now.getMonth() + 1).padStart(2, '0')}${String(now.getDate()).padStart(2, '0')}`;
  const outPath = join(DESKTOP, `小满CRM客户执行方案_${ts}.docx`);
  const buffer = await Packer.toBuffer(doc);
  writeFileSync(outPath, buffer);
  console.log(`\n✅ 文档已保存到桌面: ${outPath}`);
  return outPath;
}

build().catch(err => { console.error('\n❌ 错误:', err.message); process.exit(1); });

